##Tables

#Border Collapse

<code>
table {
	border-collapse: collapse;
}
</code>

#Row Hide

hide an entire row, including its height
<code>
tr {
	display: none;
}
</code>

and display it again
<code>
tr {
	display: '';
}
</code>

#Cell Min Size

set the minimum width and height on a table cell
<code>
td {
	height: 2em;
	min-width: 2em;
}
</code>

#Cell Align

<code>
td {
	text-align: center;
}
</coide>